18
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,800
But don't get too close.

19
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:10,800
Keep a social distance.

20
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:12,440
Just be neither humble nor arrogant.

21
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,640
Okay, I got it.

22
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,240
Wanfu.

23
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,600
Helping Mr. Tian this time

24
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,160
