40
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:10,560
Then you can secretly keep one in your mouth.

41
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,220
Don't do it in front of others.

42
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,130
Aren't you leaving?

43
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,560
I'm leaving then, Madam.

44
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,160
Right.

45
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,280
Before the sun goes down,

46
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,020
