47
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:32,240
Or they will get damp.

48
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,800
Also, tell Master

49
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,440
that under the crooked tree,

50
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,840
