54
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,200
I'm leaving.

55
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,440
That's life.

56
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,400
That's life.

57
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:09,000
That's life.

58
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,480
Master.

59
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:19,640
I don't understand. If you want to demolish the factory,

60
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,769
