66
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:32,800
Cooperate with him

67
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,440
to build a new Tailai Machinery Factory.

68
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,300
To build a factory at the new site,

69
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:39,600
