72
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,640
The usual.

73
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:47,880
I understand.

74
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,800
This way, we can

75
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:52,159
