83
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:13,880
Chencang.

84
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,320
The person we are going to meet later is Orlando.

85
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,680
Bribing Japanese officers,

86
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,560
and being responsible for clearing

87
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:23,120
