91
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,160
Understood.

92
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,680
Mr. Orlando.

93
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,240
This is Mr. Meng.

94
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,200
Hello.

95
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,320
Mr. Tian.

96
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,760
Let's make a long story short.

97
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,560
You are responsible for dismantling the machines,

98
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,920
I am responsible for escorting them

99
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:07,280
