135
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:57,000
The one from the Bureau of Investigation and Statistics assassination squad

136
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,120
I mentioned to you.

137
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:00,360
You met him again?

138
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,680
He reported our factory dismantling operation

139
