168
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:14,100
So I rushed to Maoshan without stopping.

169
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:15,680
Because last autumn,

170
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,080
Comrade Chen Yi in Maoshan

171
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,080
