You went to Maoshan?

174
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,640
I remember Maoshan is not far from Nanjing.

175
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:24,320
Right.

176
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,680
It's really not easy for your New Fourth Army.

177
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:29,610
Right under the Japanese's noses.

178
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,760
It's a long story.

179
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:34,560
Chiang Kai-shek...

180
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,020
Thanks.

181
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:38,920
Although he was forced to agree to our party's anti-Japanese proposition

182
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:41,400
