187
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,240
Our New Fourth Army, besides the Army Headquarters,

188
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,500
has four detachments.

189
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:55,280
Each detachment is restricted to

190
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,960
