191
00:09:57,680 --> 00:10:00,480
We are not allowed to recruit young people to join the army,

192
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:03,410
we are not allowed to collect public grain and taxes,

193
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:06,800
and we are not allowed to interfere in local administration.

194
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:07,680
Yunkui,

195
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,800
