201
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,720
So, can we fall for this?

202
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,360
No.

203
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:27,320
Comrade Chen Yi reported to the superior.

204
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,720
After getting approval,

205
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:30,240
we boldly

206
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,200
developed to the east and north.

207
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,560
But at the same time,

208
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,800
we couldn't be accused by the Kuomintang's Third War Area

209
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:37,320
of disobeying orders

210
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,920
and destroying the unified war of resistance.

211
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:41,360
So I used the name of

212
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:43,840
the Nuoxi Anti-Japanese Advance Column

213
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,120
all the way north,

214
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,500
