220
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:57,380
I am the commander of the Advance Column.

221
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,840
Commander!

222
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:01,840
Yunkui.

223
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:04,280
But as soon as I arrived in Jiangbei,

224
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:07,160
I heard the great name of Dougui.

225
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:09,200
I guessed it was your team.

226
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,900
So I dressed like this.

227
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:13,280
Firstly, I wanted to play a joke on you.

228
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,680
Secondly, I wanted to see

229
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,720
if your famous Dougui

230
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,120
lives up to its reputation.

231
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:20,040
How is your reconnaissance ability?

232
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:21,680
Sure enough, as soon as I got here,

233
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:23,320
I was detained by you.

234
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,800
Thanks for the compliment.

235
00:11:25,800 --> 00:11:26,920
But don't be too proud.

236
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:28,040
Although you are a commander now,

237
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:30,160
I tell you, I, Zhang,

238
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,890
am the commander of Dougui.

239
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:35,080
Let's talk about business.

240
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,760
Now, your Advance Column,

241
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:37,680
how many guns

242
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:39,410
and how many people do you have?

243
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,840
Our Advance Column has more than 300 people

244
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:42,920
and more than 400 guns.

245
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,960
We fought two small victorious battles.

246
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,320
This is on the military level.

247
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,880
But my real purpose

248
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:50,040
is to unite

249
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:51,360
anti-Japanese armed forces like yours.

250
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,440
Lead the whole area by pointing out,

251
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,600
accumulate small victories into big ones, and jointly resist Japan.

252
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,360
Fight the Japanese together.

253
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,120
Fight the Japanese together.

254
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,480
Together.

255
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,490
Yunkui, do you know?

256
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,560
In the face of this battle...

257
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:07,880
The loss for our China is just too great.

258
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,050
Last winter in Northern Anhui,

259
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,340
inside a small grocery store,

260
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,740
I thought I'd buy a roasted sweet potato.

261
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:15,840
Just as I took it,

262
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,120
I felt this paper

263
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,440
was somehow not right.

264
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:21,680
I looked closely.

265
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,160
Guess what it was.

266
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:26,480
It was a Song Dynasty edition book.

267
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,520
I was instantly shocked.

268
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:29,560
I asked the ma'am,

269
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:31,320
where did you get this book?

270
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:33,320
The ma'am said, "You want it?

271
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,200
Come with me."

272
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,850
She took me to the backyard.

273
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:38,400
Guess what I saw in the backyard.

274
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:43,280
It was full of rare books from the Song, Yuan, Ming, and Qing Dynasties.

275
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,450
And right in the corner,

276
00:12:45,560 --> 00:12:47,880
there was a large amount of Ming Dynasty furniture,

277
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:49,140
all chopped to pieces,

278
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,900
ready to be used as firewood for cooking.

279
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:53,440
It's truly a pity.

280
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:55,480
So building a new China

281
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:58,080
and expelling the Japanese invaders,

282
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,810
this is no longer just a slogan,

283
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:02,120
but an action with no time to lose.

284
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,520
Brother Yufeng.

285
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:11,160
I have a suggestion.

286
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,460
If your Advance Column

287
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:15,000
wants to establish a firm foothold,

288
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,800
the first step

289
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:16,600
is to take

290
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:18,000
Sanhuang Village.

291
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:19,120
Right.

292
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,700
Because in Sanhuang Village,

293
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:24,040
the forces of the Japanese and puppets are relatively weak.

294
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:26,800
Besides, after taking Sanhuang Village,

295
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,760
the two of us can join hands

296
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:30,360
and then proceed to take

297
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,440
Xikou Town.

298
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:32,440
Spot on.

299
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:36,880
I can see through these first two steps.

300
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,160
For this third step,

301
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,880
you have to give me some advice.

302
00:13:42,880 --> 00:13:45,360
Brother Yunkui, I understand your confusion.

303
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,320
In such an ungoverned area,

304
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:49,200
anti-Japanese armed forces

305
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:52,120
can be said to spring up like mushrooms.

306
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:54,040
Then unified leadership

307
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:56,760
will appear both arduous and dangerous.

308
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,000
I agree.

309
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:59,680
The roving bandit mentality of heroes from all sides right now

310
00:13:59,680 --> 00:14:00,940
is still very serious.

311
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,080
Their fighting style

312
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,560
still remains at waving flags, shouting,

313
00:14:03,560 --> 00:14:04,720
and pitching camps.

314
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,680
So as for what the current war

315
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,600
actually is,

316
00:14:07,640 --> 00:14:08,880
they have no understanding at all.

317
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:09,960
So they need a

318
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:13,080
long-term, patient ideological education.

319
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:15,840
Doesn't Chiang Kai-shek always emphasize that

320
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,840
resisting Japan is the government's business?

321
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,000
You commoners

322
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:21,440
just need to provide money and grain.

323
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,600
For us, this

324
00:14:23,880 --> 00:14:25,600
is a one-sided war policy.

325
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:28,920
What we practice is a comprehensive war of resistance.

326
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:31,440
We must fully mobilize the power of the masses.

327
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:33,970
Only then will the final victory belong to us.

328
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:36,360
Of course, these two policies

329
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:38,720
will face a long-term struggle in the future.

330
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:39,680
Anyway, Brother Yufeng,

331
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:40,800
your coming here

332
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:42,680
is like welcome rain after a long drought to me.

333
00:14:42,680 --> 00:14:44,400
To be honest, right now,

334
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:46,040
training the troops

335
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:47,440
gives me a real headache.

336
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,120
Besides these normal skills like shooting,

337
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:50,840
throwing grenades,

338
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:51,770
and bayoneting,

339
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:53,290
which are basic skills,

340
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,920
we need to further improve

341
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:57,280
our specific combat capabilities in mobile warfare.

342
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:59,240
How to utilize the terrain and features,

343
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,720
along with technical and tactical joint training,

344
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,000
is very important.

345
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,520
There are also guerrilla tactics.

346
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,680
I don't quite understand them either,

347
00:15:04,680 --> 00:15:06,010
and I am still learning.

348
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,840
You have to help me with this.

349
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:08,770
I am duty-bound.

350
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:09,880
Deal.

351
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:13,250
So now we are in a stalemate.

352
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,800
How should we fight this battle?

353
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:16,440
We absolutely shouldn't fight head-on,

354
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,640
but break up the whole into parts,

355
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:19,400
and immediately infiltrate the enemy's flanks.

356
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:20,760
Let me give you an example.

357
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:21,720
For example, right here,

358
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,240
when we besiege the enemy to attack their reinforcements,

359
00:15:23,240 --> 00:15:24,560
if our assault is thwarted,

360
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:26,840
we shouldn't continue the stalemate with them.

361
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:28,570
This is our guerrilla warfare.

362
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:30,640
Not this head-on fortress warfare.

363
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,000
To fight this assault,

364
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,320
we've been fighting for four hours,

365
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,520
but the enemy's motorized troops

366
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:35,640
are coming to reinforce immediately.

367
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:36,840
What should we do now?

368
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:39,080
Deploy to the middle route immediately

369
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,570
and set up an ambush.

370
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:42,080
Judge the enemy's approach.

371
00:15:42,080 --> 00:15:44,480
For example, if they come to reinforce here

372
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:46,280
from both the east and west routes,

373
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:48,840
then we quickly ambush them on both routes

374
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:50,360
and catch them off guard.

375
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,780
Chairman Mao once summarized our

376
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:54,880
sixteen-character formula for guerrilla warfare.

377
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:57,440
The enemy advances, we retreat; the enemy camps, we harass.

378
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,920
When the enemy is tired, we attack; when the enemy retreats, we pursue.

379
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:01,200
This is guerrilla warfare.

380
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,320
Do you all understand?

381
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,050
Understood.

382
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,200
Good.

383
00:16:04,800 --> 00:16:05,280
Good.

384
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:37,290
Mr. Tian,

385
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:38,880
this is today's invoice.

386
00:16:39,680 --> 00:16:40,560
I saw with my own eyes

387
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:42,420
Engineer Zhao boarding the ship.

388
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,720
He departed from the pier in the International Settlement.

389
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:46,280
He said when he arrives in Haiphong, Vietnam,

390
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:47,740
he will send us a telegram.

391
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:51,560
When will the shipment be finished?

392
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:54,720
There's about 120 tons left.

393
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:58,080
It should be finished by early September

394
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:00,920
or early October of the lunar calendar.

395
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:04,839
No, it must be earlier.

396
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:09,400
The key is that the part from Pudong to Puxi

397
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,720
is too dangerous.

398
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:15,839
The longer we delay, the more dangerous it gets.

399
00:17:15,839 --> 00:17:18,240
Kudo is coming to see me tomorrow.

400
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:20,410
He must be coming to rush me.

401
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:23,040
Go find Orlando and tell him

402
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:25,640
it must be shipped before the Mid-Autumn Festival.

403
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:27,920
I can increase the price by 10% for him.

404
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:28,840
Go quickly.

405
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,960
We can't give him any more money.

406
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:32,440
He has already taken

407
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,900
more than 500,000 from us.

408
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,360
If you tell him to expedite it now,

409
00:17:35,360 --> 00:17:36,760
he will definitely ask for an exorbitant price.

410
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:38,420
He might not even agree to 10%.

411
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:39,840
Can you ship it?

412
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:43,720
Okay, I'll try to bargain with him.

413
00:17:44,520 --> 00:17:45,640
But sir,

414
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:48,410
we have no money in our account.

415
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,020
Go contact someone

416
00:17:58,600 --> 00:18:00,880
to sell the match factory in the French Concession.

417
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:01,880
The match factory

418
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,200
cannot be sold.

419
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:04,360
Our most profitable business right now

420
00:18:04,360 --> 00:18:05,560
is the match factory.

421
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:06,780
Can you ship it?

422
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:07,720
Then think about it,

423
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:09,120
if something goes wrong with the transportation

424
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:10,160
and we've also sold the match factory,

425
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:12,290
we'll be completely out of resources.

426
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:39,280
Go, take this.

427
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:42,040
Go see Orlando and bargain with him.

428
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:45,440
If this can cover 100,000,

429
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,120
we won't sell the match factory for now.

430
00:18:47,120 --> 00:18:48,880
We can still maneuver for a while.

431
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:49,720
Go.

432
00:18:52,320 --> 00:18:54,160
Can this bottle cover 100,000?

433
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:56,880
Its value is far more than 100,000.

434
00:18:58,240 --> 00:19:00,760
Is this thing really worth that much?

435
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:09,320
No, it's not, Master.

436
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,440
I...

437
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:17,840
Go contact them

438
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,930
and sell the match factory.

439
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,120
Master, I...

440
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:25,240
Hurry up, Wanfu.

441
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:11,800
Tian.

442
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:13,040
Kudo.

443
00:20:16,560 --> 00:20:18,600
Tian, let me introduce you.

444
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:22,480
These are my colleagues from the Central China Development Company,

445
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,480
Furukawa Kiyoshi,

446
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:26,040
and his assistant Kakutani.

447
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:27,320
Hello, Mr. Tian.

448
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,680
Hello, Mr. Furukawa.

449
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:30,970
Hello, Ms. Ding.

450
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:33,000
Setsuko brought you a gift.

451
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:36,160
A gift from me.

452
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:37,080
Thank you.

453
00:20:38,600 --> 00:20:39,460
Please come in.

454
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:44,240
Tian,

455
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:46,360
Mr. Furukawa and I

456
00:20:46,560 --> 00:20:48,480
are really looking forward to

457
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:50,410
the new Tailai Machinery Factory.

458
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:52,780
I'm looking forward to it too.

459
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:59,880
How is the current progress?

460
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,120
Mr. Kudo,

461
00:21:03,280 --> 00:21:05,400
for our newly built Tailai Machinery Factory,

462
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:07,060
we are currently dismantling

463
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:09,960
the usable old machines from the old factory,

464
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:12,160
then refurbishing and repairing them.

465
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,000
This work is underway.

466
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:16,200
Then we just have to wait for

467
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:18,000
some original German parts to arrive.

468
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,560
Then we can continue our work.

469
00:21:19,560 --> 00:21:21,560
Actually, the most important thing is

470
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:23,720
the large stamping machine

471
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:25,600
Mr. Tian newly ordered from Germany.

472
00:21:25,600 --> 00:21:27,880
Due to the sudden outbreak of war in Europe,

473
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:29,320
ocean shipping has been suspended,

474
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:30,780
which disrupted our plan.

475
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:32,120
But don't worry.

476
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:34,280
The cargo is already at sea.

477
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:36,080
Once the machine arrives,

478
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:38,920
we will start installing and testing it immediately.

479
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,850
But there are still some problems.

480
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:43,760
That is, the prices of some of our raw materials

481
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,100
have suddenly gone up.

482
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,560
Mr. Tian is actively

483
00:21:47,560 --> 00:21:48,720
raising new funds.

484
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,200
I believe this problem

485
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,520
will be solved very soon.

486
00:21:51,520 --> 00:21:53,360
Can the Xintailai Machinery Factory

487
00:21:53,360 --> 00:21:55,620
start operating by the end of this month?

488
00:21:56,760 --> 00:21:57,720
No.

489
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:03,040
Tian, you promised me

490
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:05,610
that the new Tailai Machinery Factory

491
00:22:05,800 --> 00:22:09,600
would start operating on the Mid-Autumn Festival, September 27th.

492
00:22:10,120 --> 00:22:11,640
And you promised me

493
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,240
that you would definitely catch

494
00:22:13,240 --> 00:22:15,500
the arsonist at the Pudong Soap Factory.

495
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,690
That was the original plan,

496
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:20,040
to start on the Mid-Autumn Festival, September 27th.

497
00:22:20,040 --> 00:22:21,320
Blame Hitler.

498
00:22:21,560 --> 00:22:23,000
No one in the world expected

499
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:25,280
him to suddenly launch a blitzkrieg on September 1st

500
00:22:25,280 --> 00:22:26,400
to occupy Poland.

501
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,040
The outbreak of the European war

502
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:29,920
delayed my machine.

503
00:22:30,560 --> 00:22:32,640
Why don't you call Moustache and ask him?

504
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:33,480
You can ask him

505
00:22:33,600 --> 00:22:35,280
why he didn't launch the blitzkrieg

506
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:36,920
after September 27th.

507
00:22:46,080 --> 00:22:48,520
The world situation is changing rapidly.

508
00:22:48,760 --> 00:22:52,680
The situation in Europe is even more unpredictable.

509
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:55,480
But in any case,

510
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:58,840
I think the prospects for our cooperation are

511
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:00,880
getting brighter and brighter.

512
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:02,120
Of course.

513
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:04,400
To be honest,

514
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:07,160
for this new Tailai Machinery Factory,

515
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:09,200
I put in all my working capital

516
00:23:09,600 --> 00:23:12,060
and sold some properties in the concession.

517
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:13,400
You know me.

518
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,880
If I don't do it, I don't.

519
00:23:14,880 --> 00:23:16,810
But if I do, I'll do it beautifully.

520
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,520
I know that very well.

521
00:23:19,040 --> 00:23:21,840
But Tian, since we are cooperating,

522
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:24,560
why are you fighting alone

523
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:26,410
and working in a vacuum?

524
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:30,200
Mr. Furukawa has a lot of resources.

525
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:34,200
He is willing to provide all the help you need.

526
00:23:35,720 --> 00:23:36,960
May I ask,

527
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:39,880
what exactly does Mr. Furukawa do?

528
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:46,560
Mr. Tian is a friend,

529
00:23:46,840 --> 00:23:48,440
so there's no need to hide it.

530
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:52,850
Mr. Furukawa is the military representative

531
00:23:53,120 --> 00:23:57,400
of the Central China Expeditionary Army stationed at the Central China Development Company.

532
00:23:57,400 --> 00:23:59,360
Mr. Kakutani is his adjutant.

533
00:24:08,520 --> 00:24:10,800
Tian, I know your temper.

534
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:15,160
So I specially asked them to wear casual clothes today.

535
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:19,040
This is also to show their utmost respect for you.

536
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:22,060
Mr. Furukawa is here today

537
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:25,120
just to confirm when the new Tailai Machinery Factory

538
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:27,160
can start operating.

539
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:30,440
If we can't confirm it today,

540
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:32,760
will you come in military uniforms

541
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:35,060
with soldiers and guns next time?

542
00:24:35,520 --> 00:24:36,400
Mr. Tian.

543
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:39,040
I'm just here to fulfill my duty.

544
00:24:40,120 --> 00:24:41,000
Kudo.

545
00:24:41,280 --> 00:24:43,280
We agreed beforehand

546
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:46,380
on an equal and civilized commercial cooperation.

547
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:48,600
What is this?

548
00:24:49,400 --> 00:24:51,480
Mr. Tian, I am a soldier.

549
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:53,240
I am only interested in time.

550
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:55,920
Please clearly tell me the exact start time.

551
00:24:59,560 --> 00:25:01,760
Mr. Furukawa, well, I...

552
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,880
Let me handle this, okay?

553
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:13,880
Tian, I promised you.

554
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:17,000
Everything in the factory is up to you.

555
00:25:17,360 --> 00:25:19,200
I've been explaining to them.

556
00:25:19,600 --> 00:25:22,260
You don't like others interfering in your work.

557
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:24,720
No one should interfere.

558
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:26,330
Until the day of operation,

559
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:28,680
everyone will unveil it together.

560
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,480
But the problem is

561
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:34,720
the start date has been repeatedly delayed.

562
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:35,800
Tian.

563
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:38,080
Don't test everyone's patience.

564
00:25:38,600 --> 00:25:40,680
Delays will only cause trouble.

565
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,160
Kudo.

566
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,200
We are old classmates.

567
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:47,800
We've been classmates for over a decade. You know me.

568
00:25:47,800 --> 00:25:49,080
You should trust me.

569
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:50,640
Kudo.

570
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:52,840
What is this guy saying?

571
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:55,480
Is he hiding something?

572
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:58,280
Is there a problem with his factory?

573
00:25:58,520 --> 00:26:01,480
We need an on-site inspection.

574
00:26:02,040 --> 00:26:02,960
Tell him that.

575
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:07,400
Tian.

576
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:11,480
Your attitude has made Mr. Furukawa very dissatisfied.

577
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:14,920
He says you change the subject.

578
00:26:15,320 --> 00:26:16,240
If so,

579
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:18,720
he worries there's a problem with your factory.

580
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:19,880
If necessary,

581
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,800
he will go and inspect it.

582
00:26:26,040 --> 00:26:28,360
Tian, the Xintailai Machinery Factory

583
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:30,600
is a model enterprise of

584
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,280
the Central China Development Company.

585
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:34,240
Even Tokyo is looking forward to it.

586
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:35,640
On the day of the ribbon-cutting ceremony,

587
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:37,320
Kōain Tokyo Headquarters

588
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:41,740
and the Central China Liaison Department will send key officials to attend.

589
00:26:42,000 --> 00:26:43,560
Tian, you should know

590
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:47,400
that I've been bearing all the pressure for you.

591
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:56,480
Okay. October 12th.

592
00:26:56,840 --> 00:26:59,080
I checked the almanac. It's an auspicious day.

593
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:01,840
All machines will be installed that day

594
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:04,200
for opening and trial run.

595
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:07,720
Trial operations can begin on October 12th.

596
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,200
Okay, understood.

597
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:12,600
It's a deal.

598
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:14,960
It's a deal.

599
00:27:15,120 --> 00:27:16,600
Then on October 12th,

600
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:20,600
let's attend the ribbon-cutting ceremony together.

601
00:27:20,840 --> 00:27:21,920
Have a drink too.

602
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:22,920
No, thanks.

603
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:24,440
It's a deal.

604
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,240
Cheers.

605
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:26,640
It's a deal.

606
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:33,360
Tian.

607
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:36,360
I remember the last time Setsuko and I visited your home.

608
00:27:36,360 --> 00:27:38,690
It was the Mid-Autumn Festival last year.

609
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:41,440
Time really changes everything.

610
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:43,200
Today is very meaningful

611
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:45,090
and worth celebrating.

612
00:27:45,240 --> 00:27:45,800
Yes.

613
00:27:46,720 --> 00:27:47,280
Good.

614
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:50,440
Then let's ask Ms. Ding

615
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:53,160
to sing us a song today, shall we?

616
00:27:58,160 --> 00:27:59,240
I...

617
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:02,040
I can't sing.

618
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:07,680
Mr. Kudo,

619
00:28:08,040 --> 00:28:09,960
Ms. Ding is tone-deaf.

620
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:11,120
How about this?

621
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:13,840
I'll sing a folk song from my hometown

622
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,660
to entertain everyone, okay?

623
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:17,400
Who are you?

624
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:24,760
Last time, it was my wife Setsuko

625
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:26,600
who sang for everyone.

626
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:29,920
So today, let's have Ms. Ding

627
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:33,520
sing our Japanese folk song for us.

628
00:28:33,760 --> 00:28:35,880
Do you know 'Red Dragonfly'?

629
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:38,080
No.

630
00:28:40,760 --> 00:28:42,080
I will teach you.

631
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:55,080
Red dragonfly in the sunset glow.

632
00:28:55,840 --> 00:28:56,680
Come on.

633
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:08,880
Red dragonfly in the sunset glow.

634
00:29:10,400 --> 00:29:15,240
Red dragonfly in the sunset glow.

635
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:17,040
Let me do it.

636
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:21,660
I know how to sing 'Red Dragonfly'. I'll sing it.

637
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:38,280
Red dragonfly in the sunset glow,

638
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:42,720
please tell me.

639
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:44,240
Sing it

640
00:29:47,320 --> 00:29:48,640
in Japanese.

641
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:50,400
Don't speak.

642
00:29:50,440 --> 00:29:51,000
Yes.

643
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:52,440
Mr. Tian,

644
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:55,160
we are friendly collaborators now.

645
00:29:55,520 --> 00:29:56,650
A new relationship.

646
00:29:56,800 --> 00:29:59,000
Please make sure to adapt to it.

647
00:29:59,520 --> 00:30:00,720
Japanese folk songs

648
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:03,400
are best sung in Japanese.

649
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:20,960
Okay.

650
00:30:25,080 --> 00:30:35,320
Red dragonfly in the sunset glow.

651
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:40,760
I met you in my childhood.

652
00:30:40,760 --> 00:30:45,360
Which day was that?

653
00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:50,080
Taking a small basket to the mountain,

654
00:30:50,120 --> 00:30:54,320
mulberry trees were green like shade.

655
00:30:55,480 --> 00:31:00,040
Picking mulberries and putting them in the basket,

656
00:31:00,040 --> 00:31:04,680
was it just an illusion?

657
00:31:06,840 --> 00:31:16,800
The fifteen-year-old sister married far away.

658
00:31:18,880 --> 00:31:23,320
She left her hometown and couldn't return for a long time.

659
00:31:23,320 --> 00:31:28,840
News of her is also remote.

660
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:41,360
Red dragonfly in the sunset glow,

661
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:50,800
resting on the tip of the bamboo pole.

662
00:31:51,440 --> 00:32:00,120
Red dragonfly in the sunset glow.

663
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:04,600
I met you in my childhood.

664
00:32:04,600 --> 00:32:09,200
What day was that?

665
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:12,960
How was it?

666
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:14,240
Did you see Lao Xie and Fu Fan?

667
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:14,840
Yes.

668
00:32:15,040 --> 00:32:16,440
They told me the battle in Sanhuang Village

669
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,840
was fought beautifully.

670
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:18,940
She also told me

671
00:32:19,040 --> 00:32:20,320
that Commander Xie is willing to cooperate with us

672
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:22,280
to launch a surprise attack on the Japanese stronghold in Xikou Town together.

673
00:32:22,280 --> 00:32:23,840
The situation has been investigated clearly.

674
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,800
There are no more than 50 Japanese soldiers in the town.

675
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:28,160
The main force of the enemy has been transferred to the frontline.

676
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:30,360
Xikou Town is maintained by a squadron of puppet troops.

677
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:32,720
The squadron leader of the puppet troops is a gang member.

678
00:32:32,720 --> 00:32:34,120
He is doing smuggling business

679
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:36,160
with the buddies of the surrounding guerrilla forces.

680
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,480
Commander Xie also got their deployment map

681
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,840
through the gang.

682
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:39,600
This one.

683
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:40,200
Yes.

684
00:32:40,360 --> 00:32:41,760
I've been waiting for it.

685
00:32:45,080 --> 00:32:45,800
Good.

686
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,720
Sister Fu Fan also said

687
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:54,080
Commander Xie has their internal intelligence.

688
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:54,920
What intelligence?

689
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:57,240
The Japanese and puppet troops stationed in Xikou

690
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:59,120
will change their defense during the Mid-Autumn Festival.

691
00:32:59,120 --> 00:33:01,440
At this time, the Japanese troops in the town will be weak.

692
00:33:01,440 --> 00:33:03,770
So they plan to fight a battle at this time.

693
00:33:03,840 --> 00:33:05,200
They want to take joint action with us

694
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:07,060
during the Mid-Autumn Festival.

695
00:33:10,280 --> 00:33:12,160
We can't do this on our own.

696
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:14,600
We have to bring Ge Zhancheng in

697
00:33:14,600 --> 00:33:17,200
and let him lead the 18th Detachment to join us.

698
00:33:20,320 --> 00:33:23,080
The other day, under the willow tree by the door,

699
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:24,460
I saw a group of kids

700
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:26,090
singing and playing games.

701
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:30,160
They were singing, 'The sky is dim, the earth is dark,

702
00:33:30,520 --> 00:33:32,720
anti-Japanese armies are everywhere.

703
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:34,610
They don't fight the Japanese,

704
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:37,040
but only bully the peasants.'

705
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:38,760
Others sang,

706
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,610
'Central Army, fleeing refugees.

707
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:43,440
The 18th Detachment, begging for food.

708
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:45,200
Advance Column, fighting the war.'

709
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,460
I've heard about that.

710
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:47,240
That day,

711
00:33:47,520 --> 00:33:49,880
I was with Ge Zhancheng talking about guerrilla warfare.

712
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:52,160
He said, 'If the enemy is strong, we evade; if the enemy is weak, we attack.'

713
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:52,820
As a result,

714
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:55,160
the kids were singing this right next to him.

715
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,360
No one knew who he was.

716
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:58,040
For a commander like him,

717
00:33:58,160 --> 00:33:59,280
where could he hide his face?

718
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:00,400
He was furious.

719
00:34:00,840 --> 00:34:02,720
He said if he ran into the Japanese again,

720
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:03,320
Report.

721
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:05,200
I just came back from Ge Zhancheng.

722
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:07,080
About you discussing attacking the Japanese stronghold with him,

723
00:34:07,080 --> 00:34:07,880
he has made up his mind.

724
00:34:07,880 --> 00:34:09,440
He's willing to bring all the brothers of the 18th Detachment

725
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,770
and follow your orders.

726
00:34:12,560 --> 00:34:13,960
Good. Follow my orders.

727
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:16,159
Go invite Ge Zhancheng and You.

728
00:34:16,159 --> 00:34:17,800
Tell them we need to have a meeting

729
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:18,920
to prepare for the Mid-Autumn Festival operation.

730
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:19,449
Yes, sir.

731
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:26,940
Is your gun easy to reassemble once taken apart?

732
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:28,080
Yes.

733
00:34:34,280 --> 00:34:37,000
It's hard to fight, and it's hard to make peace.

734
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:39,040
Fighting the war can save the country,

735
00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:40,400
and so can peace.

736
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:43,560
If fighting the war can truly save the country,

737
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,520
we can go forward without hesitation,

738
00:34:45,520 --> 00:34:47,400
willing to sacrifice everything.

739
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,679
But North China, Central China, and South China,

740
00:34:48,679 --> 00:34:50,639
all the prosperous regions are lost.

741
00:34:50,639 --> 00:34:52,300
Chiang Kai-shek's method is,

742
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:54,330
'If you don't let me be the emperor,

743
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:56,560
then kill all the commoners.'

744
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:58,220
But Mr. Wang is different.

745
00:34:58,400 --> 00:34:59,640
What do you want to do?

746
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:02,530
Do you want to get promoted or get rich?

747
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:04,920
Don't you know me, Hechen?

748
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:07,840
When have I ever thought about getting promoted or getting rich?

749
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:09,300
I just started a newspaper

750
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:12,200
to attract like-minded people, enlighten the public,

751
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:15,000
and create a bright path for China.

752
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:16,650
What do you need me to do?

753
00:35:17,640 --> 00:35:18,970
Pay for building roads,

754
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:21,520
or buy sand and cement?

755
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,440
No need.

756
00:35:27,560 --> 00:35:30,200
Mr. Zhou has already arranged all of this.

757
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:32,680
I just want you to understand me.

758
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,080
Indeed, my thinking now

759
00:35:34,080 --> 00:35:36,000
has turned upside down.

760
00:35:36,680 --> 00:35:38,280
But my heart hasn't changed.

761
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:40,120
I'm still a staunch patriot.

762
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:42,160
You are always my good friend.

763
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:44,930
Step aside. Don't block my way.

764
00:35:50,520 --> 00:35:52,560
Hechen, can you stop reading that?

765
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:55,680
You keep talking. I can hear you.

766
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:59,320
Your way of dealing with the Japanese in the concession,

767
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,600
coping and stalling,

768
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,530
will soon stop working.

769
00:36:03,040 --> 00:36:04,040
What I know is,

770
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:06,160
the Japanese military won't give up.

771
00:36:06,160 --> 00:36:07,960
They will force you to work for them.

772
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:09,040
So what?

773
00:36:10,080 --> 00:36:12,240
So, instead of being forced by the Japanese,

774
00:36:12,240 --> 00:36:13,920
why don't you come out openly

775
00:36:14,240 --> 00:36:17,160
and join Mr. Wang in the peace movement?

776
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:24,280
The KMT's Sixth National Congress has concluded.

777
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:27,000
By the end of this year or early next year at the latest,

778
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:29,860
a unified central government will be established.

779
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:37,240
At that time, the provisional government of North China

780
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:39,160
and the reformed government of Central China

781
00:36:39,160 --> 00:36:40,420
will both be included,

782
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:43,100
and the capital will be returned to Nanjing.

783
00:36:57,240 --> 00:36:59,400
Who is the Mr. Zhou you just mentioned?

784
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:03,920
Zhou Fohai.

785
00:37:04,200 --> 00:37:04,880
Zhou Fohai.

786
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:08,160
Yes, the one who funded my newspaper.

787
00:37:09,040 --> 00:37:11,100
He is actually the number two figure.

788
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:13,820
He appreciates you very much.

789
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:15,410
Mr. Zhou wrote a letter,

790
00:37:18,600 --> 00:37:20,130
saying he wants to meet you.

791
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:21,000
Of course,

792
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:24,640
Mr. Wang also appreciates me very much.

793
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:29,000
But he is a leading figure,

794
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:30,920
dealing with myriad affairs every day.

795
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:31,960
So usually,

796
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:34,800
Mr. Zhou is closer to me.

797
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:37,600
Mr. Zhou wants to invite you to serve as

798
00:37:37,640 --> 00:37:40,640
the Deputy Minister of Economy in the new government.

799
00:37:41,720 --> 00:37:42,400
Hechen,

800
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,360
once you join the new government,

801
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:46,690
with him backing you up,

802
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:49,420
your business can expand as much as you want.

803
00:37:49,720 --> 00:37:50,780
Most importantly,

804
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:54,100
you won't have to deal directly with the Japanese anymore.

805
00:38:00,600 --> 00:38:01,840
Hechen,

806
00:38:02,680 --> 00:38:03,940
give me your attitude.

807
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:07,680
What attitude?

808
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:11,920
I want to say, actually,

809
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:16,200
you are very much like Mr. Wang.

810
00:38:16,720 --> 00:38:17,980
Dashing and charming,

811
00:38:18,200 --> 00:38:19,400
capricious.

812
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:22,440
A revolutionary actor, a political stunner.

813
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:26,480
You were a good person, why did you become a thief?

814
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:28,480
Is that how you see me, Hechen?

815
00:38:30,720 --> 00:38:32,760
It doesn't matter what you say about me,

816
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:34,820
but you can't say that about Mr. Wang.

817
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:37,730
I don't agree with your attitude towards him.

818
00:38:51,440 --> 00:38:52,520
Hechen,

819
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,080
do you know why I

820
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:56,080
spoke so earnestly to you today?

821
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:57,650
I don't know.

822
00:38:57,800 --> 00:39:00,200
It's because when I, Jin Qiwu, had no money,

823
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:03,300
I ate so many meals from you, Tian Jiatai.

824
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:04,600
I have a conscience.

825
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:09,170
Let me tell you something from the bottom of my heart.

826
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,840
Your current situation is

827
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:12,840
in dire straits.

828
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:15,820
Mr. Wang's weight in the eyes of the Japanese

829
00:39:16,200 --> 00:39:18,000
makes it easy for him to make you,

830
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,920
and even easier to break you.

831
00:39:20,440 --> 00:39:21,840
I have done my best today.

832
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:23,280
What you said,

833
00:39:23,600 --> 00:39:25,200
I will not pass on to Mr. Wang.

834
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:26,860
But your attitude,

835
00:39:27,280 --> 00:39:30,000
I will report exactly to Mr. Zhou.

836
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:33,040
If you still consider me your friend,

837
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:35,020
give me a straight answer.

838
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:39,160
Are you going to see Mr. Zhou or not?

839
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:47,580
Of course I'll see him.

840
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:49,160
I didn't say I wouldn't.

841
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,160
If I don't see him,

842
00:39:50,160 --> 00:39:52,890
wouldn't I be letting down your good intentions?

843
00:39:53,600 --> 00:39:54,720
Hechen,

844
00:39:56,360 --> 00:39:59,290
if you had said that earlier, it would have been fine.

845
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:01,320
You are a good person,

846
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:06,920
why act so coy?

847
00:40:07,720 --> 00:40:09,800
Alright, I feel relieved.

848
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,260
Take your time to read Mr. Zhou's letter.

849
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:14,250
I'll go reply to Mr. Zhou right now.

850
00:40:16,600 --> 00:40:18,130
Today wasn't a wasted trip.

851
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:06,560
You are a good person, why act so coy?

852
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:46,760
Mr. Tian,

853
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:55,320
this is the latest factory dismantling list.

854
00:41:59,080 --> 00:42:01,120
Now that the machines are almost dismantled,

855
00:42:01,120 --> 00:42:03,480
what is your next plan?

856
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:11,410
The technicians from the machinery factory.

857
00:42:12,640 --> 00:42:16,160
I arranged for them to go to Chongqing in batches.

858
00:42:16,600 --> 00:42:19,600
They will use these machines to set up the factory.

859
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:23,640
What about yourself?

860
00:42:24,320 --> 00:42:25,240
Me?

861
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:30,660
I don't want to go to Chongqing

862
00:42:31,240 --> 00:42:35,440
to eat that legendary Resistance Eight-Treasure Rice.

863
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:41,260
Do you know what the eight treasures are?

864
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:46,320
Besides aged brown rice,

865
00:42:47,680 --> 00:42:52,800
barnyard grass, sand, rice husks, pebbles,

866
00:42:53,440 --> 00:42:56,760
rat droppings, and small insects.
